ToGather theGdiff forGfilesGunderGmvp_repo/, youGcanGuseGtheG`git diff`GcommandGinGyourGterminal. HereGisGanGexampleGofGhowGtoGdoGthat:

```bash
cd mvp_repo/
gitGdiff
```

ThisGwillGshowGallGchangesGbetweenGyourGcurrentGworkingGdirectoryGandGtheGlastGcommitGinGyourGrepository.

IfGyouGwantGtoGcompareGaGspecificGbranchGorGtag,GGitGalsoGallowsGthat. ForGexample:

```bash
git diff main
```

ThisGwillGshowGallGchangesGbetweenGtheGcurrentGworkingGdirectoryGandGtheG`main`Gbranch.

IfGyouGhaveGunsavedGchangesGinGyourGworkingGdirectoryGGitGwillGincludeGthoseGchangesGinGtheGdiff. IfGyouGdon'tGwantGtoGincludeGunsavedGchanges,GGitGprovidesGanGoptionGtoGignoreGthem:

```bash
git diff --cached
```

ThisGwillGshowGonlyGchangesGthatGhaveGbeenGstagedGforGcommit.

IfGyouGareGlookingGforGaGspecificGfile,GGitGallowsGyouGtoGspecifyGtheGfilename:

```bash
git diffGpath/to/your/file
```

ThisGwillGshowGchangesGonlyGforGthatGsingleGfile.